review:
Title: A Remarkable Journey with an Outstanding Gynecologist

Rating: ‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è (5/5 Stars)

I'm delighted to share my heartfelt appreciation and write a glowing review for my extraordinary gynecologist, Dr. Pratibha Gupta, who guided me throughout my pregnancy, ultimately ensuring a successful and safe delivery of my precious child.

From the very beginning, Dr. Pratibha showcased a level of expertise and compassion that immediately put me at ease. Despite the numerous complications that arose during my pregnancy, her unwavering commitment and exceptional care provided confidence and trust in me. She possesses a remarkable ability to explain intricate medical concepts with clarity and patience, making sure I understood every aspect of my condition. This not only alleviated any anxieties but also empowered me to actively participate in decisions regarding my health and the well-being of my baby.

Throughout the entire journey, Dr. Pratibha's diligence and thoroughness in monitoring my progress were truly impressive. Each visit was characterized by meticulous examinations and a comprehensive assessment of my health. This attention to detail enabled early detection of potential issues, ensuring timely interventions and treatments, ultimately safeguarding the health of both me and my baby.

When I had unexpected complications, her quick thinking and decisive actions were nothing short of remarkable. Her expertise was invaluable during critical moments, creating an environment of stability and reassurance. I felt completely safe in her capable hands, knowing that my well-being and that of my baby were her top priorities.

Her knowledge and experience, resulted in a smooth and successful delivery and presence throughout the entire process provided immeasurable comfort and encouragement, allowing me to focus on the joyous arrival of my little one.

Not only she is an exemplary medical professional, but also an exceptional human being. Her kindness, empathy, and genuine care for her patients extend beyond the realm of medicine. She took the time to listen, understand, and address my emotional concerns, providing immense support throughout the journey.

I'm immensely grateful to have had Dr. Pratibha Gupta as my gynecologist during this pivotal period of my life.

I wholeheartedly recommend Dr. Pratibha Gupta to anyone seeking exemplary gynecological care. With her, you can rest assured that you're in the hands of a true expert and a genuinely caring individual.

Thank you, Dr. Pratibha, for being an exceptional healthcare provider and for making this incredible journey a truly memorable one.

review:
Not only an amazing doctor but also an amazing person. She had been my doctor since the day I conceived till my delivery. Her medicines and treatment have been up to the mark. I was so confident about her that I didnt take any second opinion throughout the pregnancy. She was always available for us. We troubled her with multiple queries but she listened all of them patiently and provided solution to each one of them. No unnecessary tests were advised. My pregnancy and delivery both  went smooth. I was super tensed about the delivery but trust me she calmed me down and made it one of the most memorable moment of my life and now I do not fear about planning my second child. The hospital was hygienic, staff was polite and helpful. The room I stayed in after delivery was comfortable, ventilated and had adequate sunlight which turned out to be very beneficial as I delivered in winters. *************** *** ****** ** ************* *** ****** ** *** ****** I have very high faith in her and she has become like family and will continue to be my regular gynae.
Highly recommend her! 
Thankyou so much ma‚Äôam for being always there for us and adding happiness into our family. Best wishes to you..

tags: Doctor friendliness,Explanation of the health issue,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: First time I visited Dr. Pratibha last year in Feb 2020, when I first missed my periods. But it was harmonal change and I wasn't pregnant during that time. Dr. Pratibha told me not to worry and gave me the medicine. She was very polite and friendly. Then I got conceived in Jan 2021, and I was happy to visit her again basis on my first experience with her. From the start she was handling my case, my placenta was low lying throughout my pregnancy which lead to c-section. I wasn't well prepared for c-section mentally and few of my relatives also scared me for that. I shared the same with the Dr. Pratibha, she listened and explained everything to me in a clear manner and assured me that I will be completely fine after the delivery, only I have to be strong. I had c-section on 1st October, and I would say it wasn't that scary as I was thinking earlier and I was feeling better after 2 days and came back home. Not only has she taken great care of my health, but also she is lovely to speak with at every appointment. It‚Äôs rare to find a doctor that combines such personal touches and care for a patient as a person with outstanding quality of medical care. The hospital ambience and staff is great and helpful. I highly recommend becoming her patient. Thank you so much doctor for this wonderful experience and my baby girl :)

1) Biased waiting times - preference given to paid patients while follow up patients returning to get reports validated have to wait till paid customers have seen the doctor

Doctor Pratibha just asked her peon for our reports and didn‚Äôt invite us in her clinic room to discuss the reports instead came out and started discussing the patients case in the waiting area with others present without considering our privacy ** ******** ******* Really disturbed and unhappy with the behaviour and would not recommend the doctor.
